name: Tarot Made Easy (deck and book) by Barbara Moore
description: With the right guidance, the wisdom of the tarot is available to everyone. This kit provides everything you need to get started, so you can receive spiritual nourishment and practical insights the first time you use your deck. Providing intimate, supportive instructions designed to help you build on your personal strengths, Tarot Made Easy is the perfect introduction to the profound practice of tarot. Includes 78 cards and a 216 page book.
